title: Forget Normcore, Applecore is our new favourite fashion trend
text: Fashion and style Forget Normcore, Applecore is our new favourite fashion trend Among the many highlights of Apple's launch event this week was the fact that so many of the men on stage were wearing near identical casual outfits Phil Schiller, Tim Cook and Eddy Cue unveil the new Applecore collection Photo: EPA By Stephen Doig, Men's Style Editor 2:33PM BST 10 Sep 2015
